arguments.template:
<svg:g *ngFor="let circle of circles">
      <svg:g svgLinearGradient
        [color]="color"
        orientation="vertical"
        [name]="circle.gradientId"
        [startOpacity]="0.2"
        [endOpacity]="1"
      />
      <svg:rect
        *ngIf="circle.barVisible && type === 'standard'"
        [attr.x]="circle.cx - circle.radius"
        [attr.y]="circle.cy"
        [attr.width]="circle.radius * 2"
        [attr.height]="circle.height"
        [attr.fill]="circle.gradientFill"
        class="tooltip-bar"
      />

      <svg:g circle
        *ngIf="isVisible(circle)"
        [attr.class]="className"
        [cx]="circle.cx"
        [cy]="circle.cy"
        [r]="circle.radius"
        [fill]="color"
        [class.active]="isActive(circle.label)"
        [stroke]="strokeColor"
        [pointerEvents]="circle.value === 0 ? 'none': 'all'"
        [data]="circle.value"
        [classNames]="circle.classNames"
        (select)="onClick($event, circle.label)"
        [style.cursor]="'pointer'"
        (mouseover)="activateCircle(circle)"
        (mouseout)="deactivateCircle(circle)"
        swui-tooltip
        [tooltipPlacement]="'top'"
        [tooltipType]="'tooltip'"
        [tooltipTitle]="getTooltipText(circle)"
      />
    </svg:g>
